description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Cooter purrs with a rating of 93, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 279, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 3 for East, 1 for South, and 8 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90933-83182-2.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [279 Votes, Hall of Fame]
